y heart. I sat with the elders of people and I found manhood among\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38037,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/07\/29\/dawud-rich-without-wealth\/","url_meta":{"origin":35248,"position":2},"title":"Dawud on Taqwa: Faith is richness in your heart without wealth","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 29, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Muhammad ibn Yahya reported: Dawud al-Ta\u2019i, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cA servant does not leave the disgrace of disobedience to the honor of righteousness except that he will be enriched without wealth, he will be strengthened without a tribe, and he will be entertained without company.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31728,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/02\/imam-turn-around-after-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":35248,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Imam should turn around after finishing prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 2, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Yazid ibn al-Aswad reported: I prayed behind the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and when he finished, he would turn around to face us. Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 614 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u064a\u064e\u0632\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u